    href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-cleanance-cleansing-gel-400ml/\"\r\n                            ></a>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>\r\n                        This soap-free cleansing gel is designed for the daily care of oily\r\n                        as well as acne-prone skin. Rich in <strong>Avene</strong> thermal\r\n                        spring water, a super-soothing ingredient, this gel cleanses oily\r\n                        skin types without triggering breakouts and excessive oil\r\n                        production. The skin feels clean, fresh, and purified, but never\r\n                        tight or uncomfortable!\r\n                    </p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>\r\n                    <hr />\r\n                    <h3 id=\"moist2\" class=\"text-darkgreen\">Avene XeraCalm A.D Lipid-Replenishing Balm</h3>\r\n                    <h4 class=\"mt-3\">Eczema-prone skin Best selling moisturizer</h4>\r\n                    <div class=\"product-right\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; text-align: center; margin-left: 25px\">\r\n                        <a\r\n                        href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-xeracalm-a-d-lipid-replenishing-balm-400ml/\"\r\n                        >\r\n                        <img\r\n                            height=\"200px\"\r\n                            class=\"size-thumbnail lazyloaded\"\r\n                            src=\"https://static.beautytocare.com/media/catalog/product/a/v/avene-xeracalm-a-d-relipidant-balm-d-e-f-i-400ml.jpg\"\r\n                            data-src=\"https://static.beautytocare.com/media/catalog/product/a/v/avene-xeracalm-a-d-relipidant-balm-d-e-f-i-400ml.jpg\"\r\n                            alt=\"Avene XeraCalm A.D Lipid-Replenishing Balm 400ml\"\r\n                            />\r\n                        <p class=\"mt-3\">Avene XeraCalm A.D Lipid-Replenishing Balm</p>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            <button class=\"btn btn-primary text-light px-4\">\r\n                            Buy Now\r\n                            </button>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        </a>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                        <a\r\n                            href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-xeracalm-a-d-lipid-replenishing-balm-400ml/\"\r\n                            ></a>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>\r\n                        If your skin is prone to atopic dermatitis and eczema,\r\n                        <strong>Avene XeraCalm A.D.</strong> is the perfect range for you.\r\n                        This rich moisturizing balm offers instant relief from itching,\r\n                        redness, and irritation, all the while ensuring long-lasting comfort\r\n                        and eliminating signs of discomfort in just 5 days.\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <p>\r\n                        This lipid-replenishing cream is suitable for infants, children, and\r\n                        adults, and it is also formulated without fragrance.\r\n                    </p><br><br><br><br><br>\r\n                    <hr />\r\n                    <h3 id=\"cream\" class=\"text-darkgreen\">Avene Cicalfate+ Repairing Protective Cream</h3>\r\n                    <h4 class=\"mt-3\">The repairing multitasker</h4>\r\n                    <div class=\"product-right\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; text-align: center; margin-left: 25px\">\r\n                        <a\r\n                        href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-cicalfate-repairing-protective-cream-100ml/\"\r\n                        >\r\n                        <img\r\n                            height=\"200px\"\r\n                            class=\"size-thumbnail lazyloaded\"\r\n                            src=\"https://static.beautytocare.com/media/